description: The data consist of the poverty rate by the year in Maryland and the margin of error of the poverty rate from 2006 to 2012. MOE= Margin of Error for the 90% confidence interval. Source from the U.S. Census Bureau, Small Area Income and Poverty Estimates, July 2014.
